name: RSN001 Snow Rock
description:
Introduction
This is an asteroid formed after being hit, and the huge impact caused the asteroid to successfully separate from its parent planet. As away from the planet, the crust changes, the temperature plummets, and the planet gradually freezes. 

Story
In another parallel universe, a primordial planet exploded violently at the end of its life, and its substance spread outward, split to form planets of different sizes and shapes, over time and movements.
For all planets, you can click to rotate the angle or zoom in and out at will, so that you can feel these mysterious planets more realistically.
